Latebound Constants Generator (LCG) and UML Diagram Generator (UDG)
These two tools share the same code base. It is easy to see this by the similar layout and functionality of the two tools. It also means they share the same repository, so make sure it is clearly stated which tool issues are submitted for. Updating one of the tools will also update the other. They will most likely follow the same release cycle.
